                                        "},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"a+b=multiple of 3 (since to be divisible by 3 the sum of the digits of the no.(here 1+a+b+2) should be divisible by 3
)hence ab can be 03,06,09,12,15,18,........30,33,36,39,.........90,93,96,99.
Hence we can observe that there are 3 possibilities in each set of ten except in the case of  a = 3,6,9. however we overlook the fact that even ab=00 satisfies the required condition. hence in total there are 34 solutions"}]},{"type":"text","text":"



